column7: Tonight’s opening theme is clearly tribute to the Imaginary City — the opening cover is from the town’s **The Streetwalkin’ Cheetahs**, who are named after an Iggy and the Stooges lyric and have been pumping out a corresponding racket for about 30 years now. The song itself, originally by X, is about a friend of the band that left for England to hook up with the Damned’s Captain Sensible. The lore is unclear on whether the Captain was expecting that or not.
More tribute to the greatest Queen
A bit of a random codger
